      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or a donor for parts. The exterior has significant rust issues, particularly around the wheel wells and undercarriage, along with several noticeable dents and faded paint. Mechanically, it requires substantial work to be roadworthy, and the interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is sold strictly as-is for someone with the time and resources to restore it.",
