    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and truly represents the pinnacle of its model year. It has been meticulously cared for, stored in a climate-controlled garage, and shows absolutely no signs of wear inside or out. The paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior still retains that new-car feel with pristine upholstery and surfaces. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs silently, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic features function exactly as they did the day it left the showroom. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard, complete with all service records and no history of accidents or repairs.",
