    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained, reliable example that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior finish remains vibrant, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips one would expect from careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the upholstery is supple with no tears, and all interior plastics remain crack-free. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and an engine that starts eagerly every time. We have kept up with all scheduled maintenance, including recent fluid flushes and a brake inspection. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the responsive touchscreen interface, functions exactly as intended. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
